## Cache rules for static assets (Vercel / Netlify compatible)

# Hashed assets built by Vite — immutable long-term cache
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

# HTML entry point — always revalidate
/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache

# Favicon and public assets — short cache with revalidation
/vite.svg
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400, stale-while-revalidate=604800
